== Kavllea Kiteak Rodtai Darant - Mando == 
'''Why are you crowing, O Crow'''


Type: Mando 
Source: Sukhthanker, Vinayak Sadashiw. 
Literary form: Monologue / Narrative
Translated by: Sukhthanker, Vinayak Sadashiw


